                                        Cater this!                                    

Get Capriotti’s
Whether it’s a corporate event, sports party, office meeting, birthday party, or picnic Capriotti’s is sure to be a hit! We make beautiful party trays with Capriotti’s Cold Subs and Specials. And, try our new box lunches and hot Meatball bar.

