Capriotti's Sandwich Shop, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 7:58 PM ET
Hotels, Restaurants and Leisure

Company Overview of Capriotti's Sandwich Shop, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Capriotti's Sandwich Shop, Inc. owns and operates sandwich shops. It offers cold, grilled, and vegetarian subs; and cheese steaks and salads, sandwiches, kid’s meals, and other menu items. The company also provides franchising opportunities; and catering services for corporate events, sports parties, office meetings, birthday parties, and picnics. In addition, it offers products online. The company was founded in 1976 and is based in Las Vegas, Nevada with locations in Arizona, California, District Of Columbia, Delaware, Florida, Georgia, Iowa, Maryland, Massachusetts, Nebraska, Nevada, Pennsylvania, Utah, Virginia, Washington, and Wisconsin.


